{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_vrtx_01H4RLm2TdAr2NDXkCaFUYiw","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<nexus-wpe>\n# Nexus WPE Skill\n\nQuery WP Engine account data — sites, installs, usage metrics, bandwidth, visits, storage, domains, backups, SSL, users, and diagnostics.\n\n**CONSTRAINTS (enforced throughout):**\n- ONLY use Bash tool with `nexus` CLI commands\n- NO Read/Write/Edit/Glob/Grep/file tools\n- NO MCP tools\n\n---\n\n## Workflow\n\n### Step 1: Discover the right identifiers\n\nAlways resolve site and install names before acting.\n\n```bash\nnexus wpe portfolio          # List all WPE sites + installs\nnexus wpe site wpeplugintest # Details for a specific site\n```\n\n### Step 2: Get backups before destructive actions\n\n```bash\nnexus wpe backups jppwpeplugin  # List backups for install\nnexus wpe backup jppwpeplugin   # Create a backup\n```\n\n### Step 3: Run the operation\n\n```bash\nnexus wpe promote jppwpeplugistg --to production  # Promote staging to production\n```\n\n---\n\n## Key Commands\n\n### Sites & Installs\n```bash\nnexus wpe portfolio                   # All WPE sites and installs\nnexus wpe site <site-name>            # Details for a site\nnexus wpe install <install-name>      # Details for a specific install\n```\n\n### Backups\n```bash\nnexus wpe backups <install-name>      # List backups\nnexus wpe backup <install-name>       # Create a backup (blocks until done)\nnexus wpe restore <install-name> <backup-id>  # Restore a backup\n```\n\n### Promote\n```bash\nnexus wpe promote <source-install> --to <environment>\n# e.g., nexus wpe promote jppwpeplugistg --to production\n```\n\n---\n\n## Important Notes\n- Installs and sites are different: a site has multiple installs (production, staging, dev)\n- The `--to` flag for promote accepts: `production`, `staging`, `development`\n- Backup before any promote — production data will be overwritten\n\n</nexus-wpe>"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":36051,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":36051,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"1cbc076c-d2ba-48fa-8e3a-1c7858b104b7","uuid":"74ebe1d3-3a70-4cd0-807e-36d42d59160c"}
